{
  "stem": "24470.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So he came back to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And my mother was taken away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Those that were on one side were taken away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Those that were on the out-- outside-- other side, we were taken to a place called metallurgia, which was a big, big court-- inner court of a very large factory of metal.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There we gather.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we were already separated from my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That was the f-- first major shock for me, because I saw what was happening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And my mother was taken away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We never saw her again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And obviously, she was taken-- that Aktion was taken-- later, we found out-- to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother and I and my father remained in that metallurgia, in that metal outfit with many other Jews who remained.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed there for a long time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember how much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's when my memory started sort of not functioning anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But now I know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Uh, at a certain point, I was told by my friends that from that metallurgia, we were put in a small ghetto, in a limited ghetto where we were concentrated.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't remember-- I have a very severe memory block from then on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't remember where we lived together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember that we went to work again for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember going to wash windows, clean the houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father was sent with my brother to other work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They used to come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I have no recollection whatsoever where we lived, how big a room it was, with whom we lived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That is blank.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Uh, at a certain time, my father and my brother did not come back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And later on, I was told by people who saw that, who worked with them, that they were shot.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
